OL,3,C12-year-old boy hospitalised after
OL,4,Cbeing hit by car
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for information
OL,7,Fafter a 12-year-old boy was hit by a
OL,8,Fcar in Haslingden.
OL,10,FIt happened on Saturday afternoon just
OL,11,Fafter two o'clock.
OL,13,FPolice were called to Grane Road,
OL,14,Fbetween the junctions of St Crispin
OL,15,FWay and Waterside Road following
OL,16,Freports of a collision involving a
OL,17,Fwhite Suzuki Swift and a 12-year-old
OL,18,Fchild.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
