OL,3,C12-year-old boy hospitalised after
OL,4,Cbeing hit by car
OL,6,FThe child was taken to hospital with a
OL,7,Fserious head injury, where he remains
OL,8,Fin a stable condition.
OL,10,FSgt Laura Kendall, from Lancashire
OL,11,FPolice's Serious Collision
OL,12,FInvestigation Unit, said: "This
OL,13,Fcollision has left a child with some
OL,14,Fserious injuries. He remains in
OL,15,Fhospital at this time and his family
OL,16,Fare continuing to receive support.
