OL,3,C12-year-old boy hospitalised after
OL,4,Cbeing hit by car
OL,6,F"Work is ongoing to establish the full
OL,7,Fcircumstances which led to the
OL,8,Fcollision occurring and I would ask
OL,9,Fany witnesses we haven't already
OL,10,Fspoken to or anyone with dashcam or
OL,11,FCCTV footage which could assist us in
OL,12,Four enquiries to make contact with the
OL,13,Fpolice as soon as possible,"
OL,15,FEmail SCIU@lancashire.police.uk or
OL,16,Fcall 101 and quote log 735 of 18th
OL,17,FApril 2026
